      "source_id": "kjv",
      "source_url": "https://ebible.org/eng-kjv2006/PSA049.htm",
      "text": "Like sheep they are laid in the grave; death shall feed on them; and the upright shall have dominion over them in the morning; and their beauty shall consume in the grave from their dwelling.",
      "versionTitle": "King James Version"
    },
    {
      "language": "en",
      "ref": "Psalm 49:14",
      "source_id": "asv",
      "source_url": "https://ebible.org/eng-asv/PSA049.htm",
      "text": "They are appointed as a flock for Sheol; Death shall be their shepherd: And the upright shall have dominion over them in the morning; And their beauty shall be for Sheol to consume, That there be no habitation for it.",
      "versionTitle": "American Standard Version"
    },
    {
      "language": "en",
      "ref": "Psalm 49:14",
      "source_id": "web",
      "source_url": "https://ebible.org/engwebp/PSA049.htm",
      "text": "They are appointed as a flock for Sheol. Death shall be their shepherd. The upright shall have dominion over them in the morning. Their beauty shall decay in Sheol, far from their mansion.",
